      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1767451149436,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "4. Cell :\n\n- Board is made of individual NxN cells\n- Each cell has info about\n   - Jump (represent either snake or ladder we don't care)\n     When player reach a particular cell and if jump is not null we will move the player to new end position. If its\n     Ladder player will go to higher position and if its snake it will go to lower position",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4. Cell :\n\n- Board is made of individual NxN cells\n- Each cell has info about\n   - Jump (represent either snake or ladder we don't care)\n     When player reach a particular cell and if jump is not null we will move the player to new end position. If its\n     Ladder player will go to higher position and if its snake it will go to lower position",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
